        <prompt>What was the main achievement of the Washington Naval Conference?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It increased naval armaments</option>
            <option letter="b">It limited naval construction</option>
            <option letter="c">It created new alliances</option>
            <option letter="d">It started an arms race</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>The Washington Naval Conference of 1921-1922 resulted in agreements limiting naval construction among major powers, marking a significant attempt at international arms control.</explanation>
